subproject.description: The porject supports the littoral states' efforts tp halt the decline in bioresources and to restore depleted fisheries in the Caspian Sea through the implmentation of agreed actions defined in the Caspian Strategic Plan (SAP) and to fully operationalize and make the Caspian Sea's regional environmental governance mechanism sustainable.
